---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Resources | Agora" description="Download tools, posters, and guides to help build the Agora in your community.">
  
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 bg-olive-50 text-olive-900 antialiased">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-16">
      
      <header class="max-w-3xl space-y-6">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 border border-amber-200 text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-700 font-bold">
          Member Assets
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-olive-950">The Toolkit</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-olive-800 leading-relaxed font-serif italic border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-6">
          Everything you need to signal the movement and organize your local cell. Agora spreads through physical presence and shared identity.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
             <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-olive-950">01. Analog Signal</h2>
             <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-olive-200"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-olive-600 font-medium italic">For the streets, community boards, and local gathering spots.</p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-olive-200 flex justify-between items-center group shadow-sm hover:border-amber-400 transition-all">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-olive-900">The “Exit” Poster Series</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-olive-500 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">PDF / B&W / A4 & US Letter</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-olive-900 text-white text-[10px] px-5 py-2 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-amber-600 transition active:scale-95 shadow-md shadow-olive-900/10">
                Get File
              </button>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-olive-200 flex justify-between items-center group shadow-sm hover:border-amber-400 transition-all">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-olive-900">Cell Invitation Cards</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-olive-500 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">PDF / 3.5" x 2"</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-olive-900 text-white text-[10px] px-5 py-2 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-amber-600 transition active:scale-95 shadow-md shadow-olive-900/10">
                Get File
              </button>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-olive-200 flex justify-between items-center group shadow-sm hover:border-amber-400 transition-all">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-olive-900">Agora Logo Stencil</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-olive-500 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">SVG / DXF for Laser</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-olive-900 text-white text-[10px] px-5 py-2 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-amber-600 transition active:scale-95 shadow-md shadow-olive-900/10">
                Get File
              </button>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
             <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-olive-950">02. Digital Identity</h2>
             <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-olive-200"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-olive-600 font-medium italic">For the Social Network app and internal coordination.</p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-olive-200 flex justify-between items-center group shadow-sm hover:border-amber-400 transition-all">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-olive-900">Agora Brand Kit</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-olive-500 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Logos / Typography / Palette</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-olive-900 text-white text-[10px] px-5 py-2 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-amber-600 transition active:scale-95 shadow-md shadow-olive-900/10">
                Get File
              </button>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-olive-200 flex justify-between items-center group shadow-sm hover:border-amber-400 transition-all">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-olive-900">Leader Dashboard Icons</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-olive-500 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">PNG / SVG Icon Set</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-olive-900 text-white text-[10px] px-5 py-2 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-amber-600 transition active:scale-95 shadow-md shadow-olive-900/10">
                Get File
              </button>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-olive-950 p-10 md:p-16 rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl space-y-12 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-64 h-64 bg-amber-500/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full"></div>
        
        <div class="max-w-2xl relative z-10">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-mono font-bold text-amber-500 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">03. The Discourse</h2>
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">Intellectual Stewardship</h3>
          <p class="text-olive-300 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            How we speak about the movement matters. These guides help Chapter Leaders navigate the transition from “online users” to “offline stewards.”
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative z-10">
          <a href="#" class="group block p-8 bg-olive-900 rounded-[2rem] border border-olive-800 hover:border-amber-500 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-lg">
            <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] text-amber-500 font-mono">Guide</h4>
            <p class="text-white font-bold leading-tight text-lg group-hover:text-amber-100 transition-colors">Addressing the Loneliness Epidemic</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="group block p-8 bg-olive-900 rounded-[2rem] border border-olive-800 hover:border-amber-500 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-lg">
            <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] text-amber-500 font-mono">Primer</h4>
            <p class="text-white font-bold leading-tight text-lg group-hover:text-amber-100 transition-colors">Understanding Neoliberal Atomization</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="group block p-8 bg-olive-900 rounded-[2rem] border border-olive-800 hover:border-amber-500 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-lg">
            <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] text-amber-500 font-mono">Manual</h4>
            <p class="text-white font-bold leading-tight text-lg group-hover:text-amber-100 transition-colors">Stewardship vs. Subscription</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>